      <conclusions>
         <blockContainer class="explanatoryNotes">
            <heading>EXPLANATORY NOTE</heading>
            <block name="comment">(This note is not part of the Regulations)</block>
            <p>These Regulations are made in exercise of the powers conferred by section 2(2) of the European Communities Act 1972 and by paragraph 1(1) and (3) of schedule 2 of the European Union (Withdrawal) Act 2018.</p>
            <p>Regulation 2 makes minor corrections to the Urban Waste Water Treatment (Scotland) Regulations 1994.</p>
            <p>Regulation 3 makes minor corrections to the Special Waste Regulations 1996.</p>
            <p>Regulation 4 makes minor corrections to the End-of-Life Vehicles (Storage and Treatment) (Scotland) Regulations 2003.</p>
            <p>Regulation 5 makes minor corrections to the Water Environment (Register of Protected Areas) (Scotland) Regulations 2004.</p>
            <p>Regulation 6 makes minor corrections to the Foot-and-Mouth Disease (Slaughter and Vaccination) (Scotland) Regulations 2006.</p>
            <p>Regulation 7 makes minor corrections to the Welfare of Farmed Animals (Scotland) Regulations 2010.</p>
            <p>Regulation 8 makes minor corrections to the Environment (EU Exit) (Scotland) (Amendment etc.) Regulations 2019.</p>
            <p>No Business and Regulatory Impact Assessment has been prepared in relation to these Regulations, as no impact upon business, charities or voluntary bodies is foreseen.</p>
         </blockContainer>
      </conclusions>
